\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The Boston City Campus and Business College is registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training as a private higher education provider and is accredited to offer higher education programmes by the HEQC. The institution has also applied for a Diploma in Marketing Management\'2C a Higher Certificate in Event Management\'2C a Bachelor of Commerce in Human Resource Management\'2C a Higher Certificate in Human Resource Practice\'2C a Diploma in Business Management\'2C a Diploma in Human Resource Management and a Bachelor of Commerce in Logistics. \cell \pard 

